title: Whoose Party Indoor Playground for Kids' Fun
blurb: A children's wonderland with stimulating activities.
description: Whoose Party Indoor Playground is a children's wonderland, filled with a variety of stimulating and entertaining activities. Our Crazy Go-Karts offer an exhilarating speed adventure, and the sandpit invites endless imaginative exploration. The trampoline allows kids to leap and bounce freely, while the Spray Ball Machine and Ball Projection games offer creative, interactive fun. The highlight of our playground is the 6.25-meter mega slide, ensuring thrilling descents for every child. Upstairs, toddlers find their haven with age-appropriate slides and toy cars, designed for safe, specialized play for two to three-year-olds. At Whoose Party, children not only relish unlimited fun but also experience the magic of our thoughtfully crafted birthday parties.
price_display: $15 for 1 hour, $25 for 2 hours (1 adult + 1 chlid)
datetime_display: Mon - Thu: 10:30 am – 8:00 pm, Fri - Sun: 10:30am – 9pm, PH: 10:30 am – 9pm
